CONTEXT LeftResidualTypeCheck IN ENGLISH

PURPOSE CONTEXT LeftResidualTypeCheck
{+ Test that left residual succeeds when targets can be matched.
   This verifies the type checker correctly accepts r[A*B]/s[C*B] yielding [A*C]. +}

RELATION r[A*B]
RELATION s[C*B]
RELATION result[A*C]

RULE testLeftResidual: result = r/s

ENDCONTEXT
